profile:
Organizing Addict is a Professional Organizing company based in Port Colborne, specializing in Home and Hospitality Organizing - serving all of Niagara, Haldimand, Hamilton, and beyond. 

We organize the physical (and digital) spaces in your life or workplace. Our goal is to provide you with hands-on organizing and support, helping you to let go of the things that you no longer love or need. We will help you sort through and properly store your belongings, teaching you how to maintain your new system - even after we've gone.

Organizing Addict specializes in reorganizing storage systems and processes within hotels, primarily within the housekeeping department. By maximizing every inch of storage space efficiently, employees can find what they need without wasting precious time - and money!
